    "attributes": {
        "action": "Add VAT to university tuition fees to ensure consistency in education tax policy",
        "additional_details": "I believe charging VAT on private school fees while exempting universities and nurseries is unjust. I believe this policy doesn't affect the wealthy but instead punishes aspirational families who can work multiple jobs to give their children a better future. Education is education. If it\u2019s fair to tax it, then I believe it must be applied equally.",
        "background": "Remove VAT exemption from university tuition fees. I believe the current approach is inconsistent and unfair, taxing only certain stages of education.",
